      "text": "A @USCG tactical team and Marines fast rope from a UH-1Y Venom helicopter during a maritime interception rehearsal USS Fort Lauderdale (LPD 28) while underway in the Caribbean Sea.\n\nThrough Operation Southern Spear, the Department of War remains resolute in its mission to combat illicit activities in the region, working closely with @DHSgov, @StateDept, and @TheJusticeDept.\n\nU.S. military forces deployed in the #SOUTHCOM area of responsibility are supporting #OpSouthernSpear, operations directed by @DeptofWar, and @POTUS’ priority to protect the homeland. @USNavy @NAVSOUS4THFLT @USMC @MARFORSOUTH @22nd_MEU @SecWar",
